  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bbe \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 ; \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc0\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bca\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0b8e\u0ba9\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Demonstration may be held - Inspector General of Police announcement; Warning that if you break the law, you will not be watched",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Inspector General of Police CT said that the police respect the constitutionally guaranteed rights of expression and peaceful assembly. Vikramaratna has announced. He announced this by issuing a special message to the people of the country today. However, he also warned that the police would not be watching if they break the law with violence and cause damage to government and private property.",
        "The Inspector General of Police CT. Vikramaratna made this announcement directly.",
        "Sri Lanka Police respects the freedom of peaceful assembly as well as the freedom of opinion and expression guaranteed by the Constitution. Also, the police are taking all necessary measures to protect and develop the rights of the general public. In this regard, the police headquarters has given adequate clarifications to all the policemen in all the police stations of the country from time to time.",
        "It is the duty of all to act in such a way that while enjoying the rights granted by the Constitution, it does not infringe upon the rights of others. Likewise, the police, who are constitutionally mandated to maintain law and order, cannot stand by and act in violation of the prevailing law of the country, act violently, damage public and private property, and damage public and private property, as well as freedom of assembly and expression.",
        "While enjoying their basic rights, I humbly request all the public activists, political leaders and religious leaders to act responsibly by not causing damage to government private property and not disturbing government private employees in legal service."
      ],
